James ROBINSON, petitioner,
v.
OFFICE OF the CHIEF DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL, SUPREME COURT OF MISSOURI; and Elbert A. Walton, Jr., petitioner,
v.
Office of the Chief Disciplinary Counsel, Supreme Court of Missouri. No. 17-153. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 10, 2017.
